רבע / râba‛ / raw-bah'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root (rather identical with H7250 through the idea of sprawling at all fours (or possibly the reverse is the order of derivation); compare H702); 
=== Number ===
properly to be [[four]] (sided); used only as denominative of H7253; to be quadrate: - (four-) square (-d).